# fmc_key_chains (Data Source)

This data source reads the Key Chains.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "fmc_key_chains" "example" {
  items = {
    "my_key_chains" = {
    }
  }
}
```

Read-Only:

- `id` (Number) Key ID.
- `key` (String) Crypto key string.
